---
title: Beyond Meat®-Apple Stuffing Bowls with Sage Gravy
description: Everyone's favourite part of holiday dinners is the stuffing, so why not make it the star? Our Beyond Meat®, apple and potato stuffing bowl will have you longing to cozy up in front of a fireplace!
